{"tid":1708082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"塞鐵好難，不如試吓借力打力","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T16:38:23.000Z","uid":200041,"like":236,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e6695ce538380209e61ca2886d878b41de1b11","tid":1708082,"uid":200041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:58:03.000Z","msg":"各位都知罷工成功與否，第一步都係要停鐵。但係呢排黨鐵咁多便衣狗同foodpanda，又真係幾難嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 既然係咁，不如我地用另類嘅方法嚟達到同樣嘅目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 見此po者，即刻同屋企人放風話聽日一早就搞黨鐵，叫屋企人share晒俾親戚朋友知，咁樣港豬們聽日起身為咗準時返工當然揀巴士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以考慮整條thread出嚟方便share<br />\n<br />\n2. 聽日混入戲子上黨鐵同各大交通工具，適當時候心臟病發或者暈低，咁其他人就好call白車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 戲子於黨鐵上面可以配合手足快閃行動，如果班車長期服務受阻，戲子們可以一齊去車頭推開緊急門大叫：「香港人！返工！」然後叫埋乘客一齊行路軌去下一個站上地面轉車返工。或者，車尾嘅戲子可以交D戲衝上車頭話車尾聞到燶味，怕危險就當然要離開車箱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我想返工，唔好阻住我"},{"pid":"2aaebcb65e4266fcde07bda2a41fece98d2cf7b9","tid":1708082,"uid":200041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:59:03.000Z","msg":"第一次開po，希望大家唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7a27559f628ff17b97e68c04dd53714365673e","tid":1708082,"uid":200041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:59:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77f54f4effa1d4dfa786af75a2469df3eb7c92b7","tid":1708082,"uid":200041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:59:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04f7c244bc440159ec5c4f89612a5791d46dfed2","tid":1708082,"uid":200041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:59:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d8c4736ae5d93ca92903aec6689e9bd10e7eeeb","tid":1708082,"uid":144237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"推"},